Package: node-red-contrib-thermoservice
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, node-red (>= 4.0)
Description: Node-RED input node for DS18B20 temperature via ThermoService
 Polls a DS18B20 temperature sensor through the ThermoService HTTP
 endpoint (/celsius) and emits the reading as a Node-RED message.
 .
 Output message properties:
  payload  — temperature in °C (number)
  topic    — sensor hostname (string)
  sensor   — sensor hostname (string)
  rom      — DS18B20 ROM ID, e.g. 28-0123456789ab (string)
  time     — measurement timestamp (string)
